snippet.title: Emilia Clarke Not Replacing Amber Heard In Aquaman 2? - Secret Invasion Casting
snippet.description:
Emilia Clarke may be cast in a lead role in Disney+ Secret Invasion show. If that's true, will she be able to replace Amber Heard in Aquaman 2? It doesn't seem very likely...Let's discuss! Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!! #EmiliaClarke #SecretInvasion #AmberHeard
